Text: FW Reinstatement RequestRogersThe form is on the way Call me if you have questions Thanks Johnny Original Message From Terri R Page mailto Sent Tuesday October AM To Ross Johnny Subject Reinstatement RequestRogers Johnny Tracy asked me to call a Mr Ben Rogers regarding having his Amex Card Reinstated and he needs the Reinstatement Request Form faxed over to him at If you would be so kind as to send that over to him I would really be grateful Thanks bunches Terri

E Tickets Cc This message is to inform you that your eTicket is available for pickup on the th floor of the Enron building at desk B If you have any questions or feel that you have received this message in error please contact us Pickup time is between am and pm If you feel you have received this message in error feel free to contact me Thank You Corporate Travel Johnny Ross
